# 新概念模拟电路3-运算放大器的频率特性和滤波器

## 下载

### Docker

```
docker pull apachecn0/xin-gainian-moni-dianlu-3-yunsuan-fangdaqi-de-pinlvtexing-he-lvboqi
docker run -tid -p <port>:80 apachecn0/xin-gainian-moni-dianlu-3-yunsuan-fangdaqi-de-pinlvtexing-he-lvboqi
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```
